        "subject": "DDN-89 debug: reduce stack usage",
        "message": "DDN-89 debug: reduce stack usage\n\n1, libcfs_debug_vmsg2 to accept libcfs_debug_msg_data structure\n   to replace SUBSYSTEM, __FILE__, __FUNCTION__, __LINE__ and\n   cdls on the stack\n\n2, CDEBUG, DEBUG_CAPA use static libcfs_debug_msg_data\n\n3, remove the local variable in RETURN/GOTO/__CHECK_STACK\n\nChange-Id: Ieb3fcbdb388e7fdbbf67296e57fe9d45dc9fc335\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
